Eitapong'oyie Hushai Absalom


1  Neponaa Ahitofel ajoki Absalom, “Nchooki nanu mategelu iltung'ana nkalifuni tomon o are, pee aipang nanu amir Daudi kewarie. 
2  Naa kalotu nanu enetii ninye etanaure netashala, nanang'aki ninye atua enkiputukuny; ore iltung'ana ootii te nebo ninye neisik. Naar nanu olaiguanani ake, 
3  naayaki nanu iltung'ana pooki enitii anaa esiankiki narikuni ang aarikoki olpayian lenye. Aing'oru iyie enkishui o ltung'ani obo ake, ore iltung'ana pooki neserianu.” 
4  Neitiship ina kikoo Absalom o lpayiani pooki le Israel.


5  Neitoki Absalom ajo, “Empoto sii ninye Hushai ilo Alkiti, pee kining iyiook enajo ninye.” 
6  Ore pee elotu Hushai enetii Absalom, nejoki Absalom ninye, “Nji eiroro Ahitofel ajo; amaa aikias iyiook anaa enautu ninye? Tinimikias iroro naa iyie.” 
7  Nejoki Hushai Absalom, “Ore tena kata enkikoo naishorua Ahitofel neme sidai.” 
8  Nejo Hushai, “Ore ake, iyiolo nchere ore papaai lino o ltungana lenyena naa ltung'ana magil netarasutua sii, anaa olng'arurumi otooruoki nkera enyena ti ong'ata. Ore etii ina, kaarriyia papaai lino to larrabal; meirura ninye kewarie te nebo iltung'ana. 
9  Ng'ura, ore ninye taata eisudoyie ninye kewan te ngumoto nabo, arashu ti ae wueji. Naa ore ake pee ebatata embata oo ltung'ana te rasakinoto e dukuya, ore pooki ng'ae oning nejo, ‘Etii enkidaaroto atua lelo tung'ana oosujita Absalom.’ 
10  Neaku ore ninye oltung'ani opi, oikununo oltau anaa oltau lo lng'atuny, nelepori tukul te nkuretisho; amu eyiolo Israel pooki nchere ore papaai lino naa oltung'ani magilani, naa ore lekua ootii te nebo ninye naa iltung'ana oopi. 
11  Kake ore eutaroto ai naa nchere pee kinturrurrokino iyie Israel pooki, ebaiki Dan o metabaiki Beer-sheba, eba anaa osinyai le naiposha te nkumoi naa nchere, mirikoo iyie makewan olarrabal. 
12  Neaku eikipuonu iyiook shumata ninye ti atua ewueji neba anaa enetumieki ninye, paa eikidoiki iyiook ninye te wueji neba anaa enetumieki nikidoiki iyiook ninye anaa enadoiki enkoileelio enkop; ore te ninye o ltung'ana pooki ootii te nebo ninye meing'uari ninye obo. 
13  Naa tenelo ninye ajing atua enkanasa, neyau Isiraeli pooki nkeenta ina ang, nikinkurtutaa iyiook ina ang atua oerata o metaba anaa neaku metumi ninye osoit obo te ine.” 
14  Ore Absalom o ltung'ana pooki le Israel nejo, “Ore enkikoo e Hushai Olakiti naa eisidai alang enkikoo e Ahitofel.” Amu etegelua Olaitoriani pee emir enkikoo sidai e Ahitofel, pee etum Olaitoriani ayau entorroni shumata Absalom.

Eikooki Daudi neisik


15  Nejoki Hushai Sadok o Abiata lelo apolosak, “Nji o nji eikoo Ahitofel Absalom o lpayiani le Israel; naa nji o nji nanu aikoo. 
16  Ore naa taata erriwai ilkiliku entasioki entiaki Daudi, ‘Mirura taata iyie kewarie too lang'eta oo lkejek to lpurkel, kake togiroi tukul; meijori ake olaiguanani o ltung'ana pooki ootii te nebo ninye.’ ” 
17  Ore apa Yonatan o Ahima-aa neanyisho ninche te En-rogel; nelo apa enkaisiaayiani aliki ninche, nepuo ninche aaliki olaiguanani Daudi; amu meeta nchere pee etoduaki ninche ejing enkanasa. 
18  Kake etoduaa ninche enkayioni, neliki Absalom; neaku eshomo ninche pokira are aasiooyo, nepuonu enkaji o ltung'ani te Bahurim, apa oata enchorro ti oriong e nkaji enye; nedoiki ninche atua. 
19  Neya enkitok neimulumul enjing'et enchorro, neidapashaki enkano shumata enye; neaku meyiolounoyu toki. 
20  Ore pee epuonu isinkan le Absalom enetii ina kitok ti aji, nejo ninche, “Koree Ahima-as o Yonatan?” Nejoki ina kitok ninche, “Eshomo ninche aalang ereyiet.” Ore ake pee esujaa ninche neitu einepu ninche, neshukunye ninche aapuonu Yerusalem.


21  Ore pee eidip ninche aatulusoi, neilepu lelo tung'ana te nchorro, nepuo aaliki Olaiguanani Daudi. Nejoki ninche Daudi, “Tudumunye, nilo asiooyo alang enkare; amu nji o nji eikoo Ahitofel te iyie.” 
22  Nedumunye Daudi, o ltung'ana pooki apa ootii te nebo ninye, nelang ninche Yordan; ore enasirie eitu eleku obo leitu elang Yordan.


23  Ore ake pee edol Ahitofel ajo eitu esuji enkikoo enye, neirot osikiria lenye, nelo ninye ang enkanasa enye makewan. Neitobir mbaa e nkaji enye, negor kewan; neye ninye, nenukari te nkurare e papaai lenye.


24  Neitoki Daudi alotu Mahanaim. Nelang Absalom Yordan te nebo iltung'ana pooki loo Siraeli. 
25  Netipika apa Absalom Amasa shumata enjore te rishata e Yoab. Ore apa Amasa naa olayioni lo ltung'ani oji Itra le Ishimail, apa oyama Abigail entito e Nahash, enkanashe e Seruiya, ng'otonye Yoab. 
26  Ore israel o Absalom neitayu ilng'oborri te nkop o Gilead.


27  Ore pee elotu Daudi Mahanaim, ore Shobi olayioni le Nahash oing'uaa Raba oo lamori, o Makir olayioni le Amiel oing'uaa Lo-deba, o Barsilai o Lgiliadi ooing'uaa Rogelim, 
28  neyau ndapashi, o ngirran, o motioo oo nkulukuok, o enkano, o shairi, o enkurma, naidong'o, o mpoosho, o ndaiki oo mpukunot pooki, 
29  o enaisho, o engorno, o nkerra naaitung'uari eluaata te nkaraki Daudi o ltung'ana ootii te nebo ninye pee enya; amu etejo ninche, “Eeta iltung'ana esumash nenaura nenoto enkure ti ong'ata.”

